Date: Tue, 2 Sep 2025 11:02:44 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/3] Implement RCS (Rich Communication Services) support

- Add AIDL interfaces for RCS service communication (IRcsService, IRcsCallbacks)
- Implement RcsService extending BaseService with comprehensive RCS functionality
- Add RCS service registration to AndroidManifest.xml with proper intent filter
- Support RCS capabilities, availability checks, configuration, and provisioning
- Enable phone number verification and network connectivity validation
- Add required SMS permissions for RCS phone number verification
- Follow microG architectural patterns with lifecycle-aware async operations

Resolves RCS functionality issues in Google Messages and other RCS-enabled apps.
