Date: Tue, 2 Sep 2025 16:03:51 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 2/3] Improve RCS service implementation with realistic
 functionality

- Add persistent state management using SharedPreferences
- Implement proper network connectivity validation using NetworkCapabilities
- Add comprehensive phone number validation with SIM state checks
- Implement carrier-specific configuration support (Verizon, T-Mobile, AT&T)
- Add callback registration/unregistration with proper lifecycle management
- Implement realistic provisioning workflow with status tracking
- Add proper error handling with specific error codes (NETWORK_ERROR, etc.)
- Include configuration caching and reconfiguration support
- Add detailed logging for debugging and troubleshooting

This addresses reviewer feedback about overly simplistic error handling
and provides a more realistic RCS service implementation that properly
validates device capabilities and network conditions.
